    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>A Rot-Beast is a blighted boar, its hide overgrown with thorny fungal barbs and oozing lesions. Once a natural animal, it has been warped by the creeping corruption of the Ashen Woods into a frenzied predator that charges blindly at anything warm.</p>",
      "director": "<p>The Rot-Beast is a straightforward brute. It charges in a straight line for the +5 damage bonus, then gores the nearest target. Blighted Hide punishes melee free strikes. When it drops below half Stamina, Frenzy activates — it gains +2 damage and speed but becomes unpredictable, potentially attacking allies.</p>",
